{
  "stem": "4662.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I thought maybe if he's caught, they will torture him, or he'll say something that will lead them to us in that small flat.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I left the flat at once.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had false passports.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the ones that did know, they were, they were people who didn't like the idea-- didn't like the rules that were going on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they didn't take-- and if they did know, they didn't take any notice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe they didn't know, maybe they did know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We'll never know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the Jewish people?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, myself?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got-- I know we got through it-- [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Tina, ?] used to take the children to school, in case they would think there's something wrong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she used to go and bring them back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I don't think I went out of the house very much because I couldn't speak the language properly.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had an English accent when I did speak, so I couldn't really-- sometimes I used to go and visit a friend.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once we went over to the friend with my children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the train we went on was halted, and two German soldiers came out with chains around their necks.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had-- they were standing like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And women had to go this side with children, and men, this side.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, that was a newspaper that the underground used to give out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there were people who used to pass it around to people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were looking for these people, the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So everybody had to get out, and they searched you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I know my youngest son had little toy pistol, a wooden one.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I joked about the pistol.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I joked, and I had to show my identity cards.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
